dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Lung-Ch'i. In upper left margin: China city plans 1:12,500. Polyconic projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. Pinyin name for this city: Zhangzhou. Chinese place names transcribed according to the modified Wades-Giles system. With Chinese-English glossary.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1946.
